so called "show."

40:13.412 --> 40:15.581
Say, Emile, what's that on your lapel?

40:15.873 --> 40:17.541
I do believe it's the Medal of Honour, Raoul.

40:18.334 --> 40:20.461
Well, Emile. What a coincidence!

40:20.544 --> 40:22.338
I happen to have one, too!

40:22.421 --> 40:24.548
What? Where did you steal this?

40:25.174 --> 40:26.967
Oh, no. We didn't steal them.

40:27.093 --> 40:29.178
- They're from Commissioner Maynott.
- Really!

40:29.553 --> 40:30.846
Hold on! Wait, what is that?

40:30.930 --> 40:32.765
Do you hear something? I hear a voice.

40:32.848 --> 40:36.268
"If you get the Medal of Honour,
you get the best seat in the house."

40:36.352 --> 40:37.686
Sound familiar?

40:37.812 --> 40:38.854
- Albert. ..
- What?

40:38.938 --> 40:42.024
Show these gentlemen
to the best seat in the house.

40:42.108 --> 40:43.317
Why me?

40:43.400 --> 40:47.029
Enjoy the show. If you even know
what you're watching.

40:49.073 --> 40:50.366
Bye.

40:51.075 --> 40:53.661
- You two know each other?
- Oh... Yes!

40:54.495 --> 40:56.038
I mean, uh... Yes.

40:56.330 --> 40:57.706
(EXHALES)

40:57.790 --> 41:00.126
- He's such a...
-(PLAYING GUITAR)

41:01.043 --> 41:02.503
Francoeur! What are you?

41:02.586 --> 41:05.548
- Darling! He's brilliant!
- I can explain.

41:05.631 --> 41:07.550
Genius needs no explanation, my dear.

41:07.633 --> 41:10.636
I've never been so transported.
Where did you find him?

41:10.719 --> 41:12.471
He, uh... Just dropped in.

41:12.555 --> 41:15.391
