sweet, sweet voice.

41:15.474 --> 41:17.143
I'll go inform the rest of the musicians.

41:17.852 --> 41:18.894
I really don't think...

41:18.978 --> 41:21.772
History will be made tonight. I can feel it.

41:21.856 --> 41:23.274
(GIGGLES)

41:24.400 --> 41:27.987
What part of "Don't make a sound,"
did you not understand?

41:32.158 --> 41:34.493
Thank you, my good man! Thank you.

41:34.577 --> 41:35.828
Don't mention it.

41:35.911 --> 41:38.414
Come on, buddy relax! Lose the coat!

41:39.582 --> 41:41.083
(SIGHS) okay-

